import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceDetail from '../../components/sections/ServiceDetail.astro';
---

<Layout title="Benedikt Ritter - Developer Productivity Consulting">
    <ServiceDetail pageTitle="Gradle consulting">
        <p class="mb-8">
        Gradle is one of the most powerful and flexible build systems available, used by millions of developers worldwide to automate builds and streamline development workflows.
        With its versatility, it’s the tool of choice for building everything from simple projects to large-scale enterprise applications.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-8">
        With over 5 years of hands-on experience at Gradle, Inc., the company behind the Gradle Build Tool, I bring unmatched expertise to help you make the most of Gradle.
        Whether you’re optimizing for performance, modernizing your build scripts, or solving complex dependency issues, I have the experience and skills to make your build processes faster, more reliable, and easier to maintain.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Gradle Consulting Services Include:</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-8">
            <li>
                <strong>Build performance optimizations:</strong> Analyze and optimize your build to reduce execution times and improve developer productivity.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Build DSL migrations:</strong> Modernize your build scripts by migrating from Groovy DSL to Kotlin DSL for better type safety and tooling support.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Build tool migrations:</strong> Migrate your projects from Apache Maven™ or Apache Ant™ to Gradle for improved performance and modern tooling support.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Gradle Build Tool version upgrades:</strong> Safely upgrade your project to the latest Gradle version while addressing compatibility issues.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Advanced dependency management:</strong> Resolve dependency conflicts, optimize configurations, and implement advanced strategies for dependency resolution.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Build refactoring:</strong> Simplify and modularize your build scripts for maintainability and scalability.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Custom plugin development:</strong> Create tailored Gradle plugins to automate unique processes or extend Gradle’s capabilities to suit your needs.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Gradle training and adoption support:</strong> Deliver customized training sessions to help your team understand and adopt Gradle effectively, with content tailored to the specific needs and challenges of your project.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mb-6">
        Whether you’re looking to address a specific issue or achieve long-term build process improvements, I’m here to help. Let’s work together to make Gradle work better for you.
        </p>
    </ServiceDetail>
</Layout>

